div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7729b76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7729b76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.18.0 - 20-12-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"554\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/fb-ad.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-28000\" alt=\"fb ad\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/fb-ad.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/fb-ad-300x237.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-740bba1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"740bba1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Step 1: Create a Facebook page-<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-762c666 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"762c666\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Here&#8217;s how to create a Facebook page:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li>Go to facebook.com\/pages\/create.<\/li><li>Select the type of page you want to create: business, brand, or public figure.<\/li><li>Enter the name of your page and some basic information about it.<\/li><li>Choose a profile picture and cover photo for your page.<\/li><li>Start sharing content on your new Facebook page!<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b4e8db elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3b4e8db\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Step 2: Create a Facebook Ads account<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6aff301 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6aff301\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you&#8217;re looking to get started with advertising on Facebook, the first step is to create a Facebook ad account. <strong>Here&#8217;s a quick guide on how to do just that:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li>Go to www.facebook.com\/business and click Create Ad Account in the top right-hand corner.<\/li><li>Fill out the required information, including your business name, address, and phone number.<\/li><li>Once you&#8217;ve completed all of the necessary fields, click Continue.<\/li><li>On the next page, you&#8217;ll be prompted to choose your billing method and time zone. Be sure to select the options that best suit your needs before clicking Save and Continue.<\/li><li>That&#8217;s it! You&#8217;ve now successfully created a Facebook ad account that you can use to start running ads for your business on Facebook.<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-446cea7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"446cea7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Step 3: choose your objectives<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-60e067f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"60e067f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>There are a few things to consider when selecting a Facebook ad objective. First, think about what you want your ad to achieve. Do you want to increase brand awareness, get more website clicks, or drive more in-store sales? Once you know what your goal is, select the corresponding objective from Facebook\u2019s options.<\/p><p>Keep in mind that each objective has different optimization and delivery options. For example, if you choose the \u201cReach\u201d objective, Facebook will optimize your ad delivery to show it to as many people as possible. If you select the \u201cWebsite Conversions\u201d objective, Facebook will show your ad to people who are more likely to convert to your website.<\/p><p>Finally, keep in mind that you can always change your ad\u2019s objective later if it\u2019s not performing the way you want it to.<\/p><p><strong>Select traffic from the Ads objective under consideration.<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff8cae3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ff8cae3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"534\" height=\"386\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Ads-objective.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-27990\" alt=\"Ads objective\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Ads-objective.png 534w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Ads-objective-300x217.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6156b55 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6156b55\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Set Ad Duration And Budget<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b7c6694 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b7c6694\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"536\" height=\"391\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Duration-And-Budget.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-27992\" alt=\"Duration And Budget\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Duration-And-Budget.png 536w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Duration-And-Budget-300x219.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 536px) 100vw, 536px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fdf9247 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"fdf9247\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Step 4: target your audience<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72006f1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"72006f1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>As Facebook continues to grow, so does its potential as a marketing tool. With over 2 billion monthly active users, businesses of all sizes can find their target audience on the platform.<\/p><p>But with such a large user base, how do you go about targeting your Facebook audience?<\/p><p><strong>Here are a few tips:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li><strong>Use Facebook&#8217;s built-in tools.<\/strong> The platform offers a number of ways to target your ads, including by location, age, gender, interests, and behaviors.<\/li><li><strong>Get to know your audience.<\/strong> Take the time to understand who your target audience is and what they&#8217;re interested in. This will help you create more targeted content that resonates with them.<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-179d7ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"179d7ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"541\" height=\"479\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/target-your-audience.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-27993\" alt=\"target your audience\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/target-your-audience.png 541w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/target-your-audience-300x266.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 541px) 100vw, 541px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f1d45a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2f1d45a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol start=\"3\"><li><strong>Experiment with different ad formats.<\/strong> Facebook offers a variety of ad formats, so experiment with different ones to see which performs best with your target audience.<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b3b6cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4b3b6cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Step 5: Create your ad<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3febc63 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3febc63\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In the ad setup screen, you need to mention all the details like ad text, ad creative, landing page and hit publish.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6608ba2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6608ba2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"383\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Create-your-ad.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-27994\" alt=\"Create your ad\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Create-your-ad.png 383w, https:\/\/www.rankontechnologies.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Create-your-ad-204x300.png 204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 383px) 100vw, 383px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e119830 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e119830\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What to consider when creating ads on Facebook?<\/h3>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48db183 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"48db183\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Assuming you would like tips on creating a successful ad on Facebook:<\/strong><\/p><ol><li><strong>Keep your ad copy short and sweet-<\/strong> people scrolling through their Facebook feed don\u2019t want to stop and read a novel. Get to the point quickly.<\/li><li><strong>Use eye-catching images or videos-<\/strong> again, people scrolling through Facebook are quickly skimming through content. An attention-grabbing image or video is more likely to make them stop and view your ad.<\/li><li><strong>Use persuasive language-<\/strong> your ad should be convincing enough that someone would want to take the next step, whether that\u2019s clicking through to your website or making a purchase.<\/li><li><strong>Target your audience-<\/strong> whom do you want to see your ad? You can use Facebook\u2019s targeting options to narrow down who will see your ad based on factors like age, location, interests, and more.<\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa220b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"aa220b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb9e5b6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bb9e5b6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t